</fr:meta>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter><fr:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f\colon  A\to  B]]></fr:tex> be <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-000U.xml" title="Biinverse" addr="//erct/erct-000U" type="local">biinvertible</fr:link> with <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s,r\colon  B\to  A]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[h_s\colon  f \circ  s \sim  1_{B}]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[h_r\colon  r\circ  f = 1_{A}]]></fr:tex>. Then we may define a homotopy <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[h' \colon  s\circ  f \sim  1_{A}]]></fr:tex> exhibiting <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s\colon  B\to  A]]></fr:tex> as a retraction of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f\colon  A\to  B]]></fr:tex>. Therefore, we may define a <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-000X.xml" title="Quasi-inverse" addr="//erct/erct-000X" type="local">quasi-inverse</fr:link> to <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex> tracked by <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s\colon  B\to  A]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
 
   
   <fr:tree show-metadata="false" toc="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link href="foreign-erct-jonmsterling.xml" title="Jon Sterling" addr="//erct/jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:date><fr:year>2023</fr:year><fr:month>12</fr:month><fr:day>30</fr:day></fr:date><fr:anchor>10228</fr:anchor><fr:addr type="machine">//erct/unstable/454</fr:addr><fr:route>foreign-erct-unstable-454.xml</fr:route><fr:title text="" /><fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
 <fr:p>We have <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s\circ  f \sim  r\circ  f \circ  s\circ  f]]></fr:tex> by <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[h_r]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[r\circ  f \circ  s\circ  f\sim  r \circ  f]]></fr:tex> by <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[h_s]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[r\circ  f \sim  1_{A}]]></fr:tex> by <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[h_r]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
</fr:mainmatter></fr:tree>
 
